移民。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪好好奇美國點解得把口唔出手制裁？我話你知幾時先制裁、有冇可能封關、應唔應該走、幾時要走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2093986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2093986</a><br />\n<br />\n(分析)仲有幾耐入東突(新疆)模式，見到咩警告要流亡？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1980175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1980175</a><br />\n<br />\n香港簡易流亡手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/478029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/478029</a><br />\n<br />\n[借古鑑今] 中國因逃亡潮於 1951 年 2 月 15 日鎖關，香港因 BNO 鎖關的憂慮正響歐美之間蔓延！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2390806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2390806</a>"},{"pid":"e69b5cb2e297f5910cbf0cd7b43a69e3f7eabf21","tid":2396453,"uid":45991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f3d12543e474a6c72a48ebaa6495fdd67688636b","tid":2396453,"uid":10274,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"一個林鄭 玩殘成個旅遊業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"佢係無底深洞黎，無樣新野都可以再再再仆街啲"},{"pid":"101a8f37aac9aa5e45ee56d7f08a24036295ca5f","tid":2396453,"uid":360931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:13:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4709bb9aac0ce18bcca2ae403ccc63421d32ab0","tid":2396453,"uid":6777,"like":7,"dislike":31,"score":-24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"點呀<br />\n免又話開大門<br />\n唔免又話玩死人地行業<br />\n<br />\n兒登仔真係用立場黎諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74130968a3e841a01c0527efc8088b5fe8bbda2f","tid":2396453,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e4709bb9aac0ce18bcca2ae403ccc63421d32ab0","tid":2396453,"uid":6777,"like":7,"dislike":31,"score":-24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"點呀<br />\n免又話開大門<br />\n唔免又話玩死人地行業<br />\n<br />\n兒登仔真係用